languages.text: "Я убил того, кого ты так стремился призвать, на твоих глазах, и ты даже не вмешался?"
"I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"

languages.text: “我杀了你那么急于召唤的那只生物。我当着你的面杀了他，可你却连一丁点干涉的意思都没有，是吗？”
languages.original_text: "I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"

languages.text: "Ich habe den getötet, den Ihr unbedingt rufen wolltet. Ich habe ihn vor Euren Augen getötet und Ihr seid nicht einmal eingeschritten."
languages.original_text: "I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"

languages.text: «He matado al ser que tan empeñado estabas en invocar. Lo he matado ante tus propios ojos, y ni siquiera has intervenido. ¿Por qué?».
languages.original_text: "I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"

traits.locale_text: «He matado al ser que tan empeñado estabas en invocar. Lo he matado ante tus propios ojos, y ni siquiera has intervenido. ¿Por qué?».

languages.text: « J'ai tué l'être que vous teniez tant à invoquer. Je l'ai anéanti sous vos yeux et vous n'avez rien fait pour m'en empêcher. »
languages.original_text: "I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"

languages.text: 「私は、お前が召喚したいと熱望していた者を殺した。お前の目の前で殺したのに、お前は邪魔さえしなかっただろう？」
languages.original_text: "I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"

traits.locale_text: 「私は、お前が召喚したいと熱望していた者を殺した。お前の目の前で殺したのに、お前は邪魔さえしなかっただろう？」

languages.text: "Çağırmak için can attığın kişiyi katlettim. Hem de senin gözlerinin önünde öldürdüm onu. Sen de araya girmeye tenezzül dahi etmedin, haksız mıyım?"
languages.original_text: "I killed the one you were so eager to summon — I killed him before your very eyes and you did not even interfere, did you?"
